        <label>make decimation</label>
        <description>A two handed mace so heavily enchanted that it tears apart the cohesion of any material it strikes. It is forged seemingly from a single piece of metal and wielded from a handle wrapped in simple leather. Finely etched runes cover the surface of the mace, making it appear almost delicate. When held, the quality of the design is apparent, with perfect balance and solid handling despite the authoritative finality of its weight. Each blow has a chance to inflict frailty on the target, causing it to take more damage from subsequent attacks.\n\nThis weapon is enchanted and provides additional benefits to trained mages and fighters:\nMax Energy: +40\nArcane Resistance: +40%\nDamage Boost: +30%\nFrailty on hit (50%)</description>
